### Annexation

The charade of self-determination culminated on March 16, 2014, with a [referendum on the status of Crimea](/2014_Crimean_status_referendum). According to Russian figures, an overwhelming 96.77% of Crimeans voted to join the Russian Federation. This vote, held under duress and without international observation, was the justification Russia needed. The next day, the [Verkhovna Rada of the Autonomous Republic of Crimea](/Verkhovna_Rada_of_Crimea) declared Crimea's independence. Then, on March 18th, in the gilded halls of the [Kremlin](/Kremlin), [President of Russia](/President_of_Russia) [Vladimir Putin](/Vladimir_Putin), flanked by the self-proclaimed leaders of Crimea – [Sergey Aksyonov](/Sergey_Aksyonov), [Vladimir Konstantinov](/Vladimir_Konstantinov_(politician)), and [Aleksei Chalyi](/Aleksei_Chaly) – signed the treaty absorbing Crimea into Russia. The [Federation Council](/Federation_Council_(Russia)) swiftly ratified the treaty, establishing the [Republic of Crimea](/Republic_of_Crimea_(Russia)) and the [federal city](/Federal_cities_of_Russia) of [Sevastopol](/Sevastopol) as new Russian subjects.

The international community, however, refused to play along. On March 27, 2014, the [United Nations General Assembly](/United_Nations_General_Assembly) passed a resolution affirming Ukraine's territorial integrity, recognizing Crimea and Sevastopol as integral parts of Ukraine. Only 11 nations, mostly aligned with Russia, voted against it. 58 abstained. Ukraine, naturally, does not recognize the annexation. Neither do the [UN General Assembly](/United_Nations_General_Assembly), the [PACE](/Parliamentary_Assembly_of_the_Council_of_Europe), nor the [OSCE PA](/Parliamentary_Assembly_of_the_Organization_for_Security_and_Co-operation_in_Europe). It stands in direct contradiction to the findings of the [Venice Commission](/Venice_Commission). Russia, meanwhile, spins it as a "return." For Ukraine, and anyone with a shred of integrity, Crimea remains a [temporarily occupied territory](/Russian-occupied_territories_of_Ukraine).

